result.reason: Feature request from maintainer to add autocomplete/intellisense UI for variable tokens (%HOSTNAME%, %USERNAME%, etc.) in text boxes that support variable replacement, improving discoverability of 25+ available variables.
result.approach: Create a reusable autocomplete helper that lists available variables (extracted from ExternalToolArgumentParser.GetVariableReplacement switch cases) as a dropdown when user types '%' in supported text boxes. Show variable name and current resolved value as hint. Integrate into ExternalToolsWindow argument/filename text fields.
